    "## Hamming Bound\n",
    "\n",
    "A Hamming ball or radius $(d-1)/2$ has size $\\sum^{(d-1)/2}_{i=0}\\binom{n}{i}(q-1)^i$. The codeword space must have such a ball centered at every codeword such that the balls are not overlapping.\n"
